text: Ðis is þara XX hidæ boc æt mordune þæ Edwig cing gæbocode Wynsige hys þægne on ece yrfæ.
Ðis synt þa landgemero to Mordune ærest of headdam dune slade nyðer on hred burnan andlang burnan on wurf.
Þonne andlang foslace on þara ecera & heafda anlang þære heafda on ettan pæn on þonne ellemstub þonon a be ecge on þa medemunge of þære medemunge nyðer on þone ealdan wiðig.
Þonon on hnottan forð of ðam forda on þone ealdan wylle þonon eft on headdan dune sled.
